high_descs: Walk straight and reach the dining table and turn towards your right.
Take the frying pan from the top of the table.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the pan in the fridge and close the door. After some times, open the door and take out the pan and then close the door again.
Turn right and walk towards the countertop.
Place the pan on the countertop next to the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place the Pan next to the CounterTop

high_descs: Take the pan from the dining table.
Open the fridge, place the pan inside, wait for few seconds and take it out from the fridge and close the fridge.
move right, turn around and go towards the countertop
Place the pan on the countertop near the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan near the kitchen sink from the countertop

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bathtub to your left  dining  table
take  the pan in the  table
place on the  pan in the fridge
take  the  pan  turn around the  right side
put the pan  in the  counter top
anns.task_desc: take  the pan  and  put the pan  in the  counter top
